## For families across the Middle East and Africa

We are excited to offer you and your children, aged 8 - 15, the opportunity to join the IBM Family Science sessions starting on 22 July 2023.

IBM Families, please visit #family_science slack channel for registration information. External students, please register through your school.

All Sessions start at 11:00 PM GMT. Please see below for the preparation instruction for each class. If you don't have time to prepare - join us anyway and have fun learning about science! For questions, please contact Tamara.Govindasamy@ibm.com.
